plot: V.I.P. is hired by the Environmental Protection Agency's Arthur Goodwin to help transport an experimental Red Coyote terrorist movement weapon to a marine base for destruction. But Val's evil double Joan Archer has escaped from the lunatic asylum, reassembles a gang and ties up and gags Val. This allows Joan to take her place and abuse the device for revenge on V.I.P. Only Kay gets suspicious.—KGF Vissers
